{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ac2540b711","title":"和邓小平在长沙的一次谈话（节录）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b53a60fc9c","index":0,"year":1974,"month":11,"day":12,"articleId":"ac2540b711"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"82305e518c","name":"江青","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji51","name":"毛泽东全集第51卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/51-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji51":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a08d284209","type":"title","text":"和邓小平在长沙的一次谈话（节录）","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"ac2540b711"},{"id":"18288dd12f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东（以下简称毛）：你开了一个钢铁公司！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"ac2540b711"},{"id":"30ac2a1cc2","type":"paragraph","text":"邓小平（以下简称邓）：主席也知道了。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"ac2540b711"},{"id":"72a68780c7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：好！","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"ac2540b711"},{"id":"91fce5f398","type":"paragraph","text":"邓：我实在忍不住了，不止一次了。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"ac2540b711"},{"id":"22b37f9dce","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：我赞成你！","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"ac2540b711"},{"id":"fd829b573a","type":"paragraph","text":"邓：她在政治局搞了七八次了。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"ac2540b711"},{"id":"5ef2d5c1f6","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：强加于人哪，我也是不高兴的。她们都不高兴","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"ac2540b711"},{"id":"9f5052cf2a","type":"paragraph","text":"邓：我主要是感觉政治局的生活不正常。最后我到她那里去讲了一下，钢铁公司对钢铁公司。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"ac2540b711"},{"id":"6471ec2731","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：这个好。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"ac2540b711"},{"id":"6ab0896d11","type":"paragraph","text":"邓：最近关于我的工作的决定，主席已经讲了，不应再提什么意见了，但是看来责任是太重了一点。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"ac2540b711"},{"id":"ed2cb2b5e0","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：没办法呢，只好担起来哦。","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"ac2540b711"},{"id":"35d761e042","type":"paragraph","text":"CI]指江青。","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"ac2540b711"},{"id":"9bbdb75f18","type":"paragraph","text":"12]指江青。","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"ac2540b711"},{"id":"5b5b955721","type":"paragraph","text":"指当时在谈话现场的王海荣和唐闻生。","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"ac2540b711"}],"page":{"id":"e499b2104c","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"ac2540b711","start":516,"end":516}}}},"__N_SSG":true}